OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly start for many then a
OL,6,Fdry day with plenty of sunshine, this
OL,7,Fturning hazy at times due to high
OL,8,Fcloud. Feeling quite warm in the
OL,9,Fafternoon with light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA bright end to the day then
OL,12,Fa dry night with long clear spells.
OL,13,FBecoming chilly in the Argyll glens
OL,14,Fwith a touch of frost and patchy fog.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FAnother dry and bright day
OL,17,Fwith long periods of sunshine. A
OL,18,Fchilly start for many then becoming
OL,19,Fwarm by the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
