OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FHigh
OL,6,Fpressure will maintain the dry and
OL,7,Fsettled weather with sunshine at
OL,8,Ftimes. Feeling quite warm inland but
OL,9,Fcooler along coasts.
